    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个充满怪物、动作紧凑的2D类魂rogue-lite游戏中，杀出一条通往光明的道路，探索被疫病侵袭的世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战多种强大的敌人和首领</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验类魂系列的战斗机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在无限的新游戏+剧情模式中面对不断升级的挑战</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890310/extras/25a2767391643a9814836079b1ff2b3c.poster.avif?t=1769867346\" width=1170 height=682 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890310/extras/25a2767391643a9814836079b1ff2b3c.webm?t=1769867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色养成</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有武器均为单手武器，自由搭配剑、匕首、魔杖或盾牌，打造独特的构筑。（盾牌仅限左手装备）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过50种武器，每种武器都拥有独特的技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对任何敌人（包括首领）施加状态效果，如流血、中毒、燃烧、冰冻、感电、窒息、粉碎、生命溅射、黑暗或光辉打击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找大量祝福，这些独特物品将改变你的角色构筑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升角色等级以解锁更多种类的武器、装备和祝福。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >永久升级你的角色，在未来的探索中解锁更多选项。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890310/extras/db5f56942b45ab11475b1fa5e7db0d8b.poster.avif?t=1769867346\" width=1170 height=682 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890310/extras/db5f56942b45ab11475b1fa5e7db0d8b.webm?t=1769867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地图探索</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越三个随机生成的地图，面对独特的敌人、背景和随机事件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现随机事件并获得独特奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到装满祝福的宝箱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >造访商店，获取武器、装备和祝福。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过向雕像祈祷来提升生命值、法力或体力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用铁匠将多余的装备熔炼，以升级现有装备。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890310/extras/5d73470e3c888061f4bbd0395c3c9c3a.poster.avif?t=1769867346\" width=1170 height=682 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890310/extras/5d73470e3c888061f4bbd0395c3c9c3a.webm?t=1769867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
